                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17730626-16-defend204 t17730626-16-deflabel86"></join> since; I lived pretty near him for a time in Great-White-Lion-street; he lived there about two months ago. I never heard any thing laid to his charge before this.</p>
